---
Manage the threat intelligence database

Usage: tirith threat-db <COMMAND>

Commands:
  update  Download or update the threat intelligence database
  status  Show threat DB status, age, and entry counts
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help

Examples:
  tirith threat-db update
  tirith threat-db update --force
  tirith threat-db status --format json
